#Text=Ohioville creek bones are not human
#Text=Some bones that were found in a Ohioville , Pennsylvania creek are no longer said to be human according the authorities .
#Text=Children found the bones when they were swimming under a train trestle .
#Text=The bones were found in Little Beaver Creek and are said to be from a dog , deer or another large mammal .
#Text=Sources
#Text=" Bones found in Ohioville creek are n't human " — The Pittsburgh Tribune-Review , August 10 , 2008
#Text=Bill Vidonic .
#Text=" Bones found in creek to be examined today " — The Beaver County Times , August 7 , 2008
#Text=Etna motorcyclist killed when hit by tree
#Text=A tree hit and killed an Etna , Pennsylvania motorcyclist .
#Text=A truck went rolling down a hill knocking a tree down which landed on the motorcycle .
#Text=Fifty-nine year old motorcyclist , Alan Brocklebank , was sent to the hospital after the 3 p.m. accident .
#Text=He died later that morning .
#Text=The pickup driver was charged by police with drunken driving and homicide .
#Text=Sources
#Text=Bobby Kerlik .
#Text=" Motorcyclist killed in Etna when a tree hits his bike " — The Pittsburgh Tribune-Review , August 10 , 2008
#Text=" Motorcyclist In Etna Accident Dies " — The Pittsburgh Channel , August 9 , 2008

column1: #Text=" Truck Flips Down Hill , 1 Killed In Etna Accident " — KDKA , August 9 , 2008
#Text=Police dog found in Pasadena , California
#Text=A K-9 dog , aged 10 , was found safely in Pasadena , California .
#Text=The dog is a Belgian Malinois named Robby , weighing around 70-75 lbs.
#Text=The dog was saved by an unknown person on Friday morning .
#Text=The dog is in fine health and was returned to his police unit .
#Text=Sources
#Text=" Robby picked up by a Good Samaritan " — Houston Chronicle , August 9 , 2008
#Text=" Pasadena K-9 missing " — Houston Community Newspapers , April 8 , 2008
#Text=Somalian police chief dies
#Text=In Somalia a high ranked police chief has been killed in an attack that also resulted in the death of four civilians .
#Text=Grenades were involved in the attack .
#Text=This attack occurred near the Somali capital of Mogadishu .
#Text=The attack took place in a police station in the city of Alamada .
#Text=A witness said that bullets were coming from all directions , and that the attack resulted in the death of his son .
#Text=Sources
#Text=AFP . " Attack kills Somali police chief , civilians die in reply : witnesses " — Yahoo ! News , August 9 , 2008
#Text=" Somali police chief killed " — News 24 , August 9 , 2008
#Text=Cassini probe passes Saturn moon Enceladus
#Text=NASA 's Cassini spacecraft zoomed past Saturn 's moon Enceladus at just 50 kilometres above its surface .
#Text=The probe attempted to take detailed images of active geysers on the moon , which may offer evidence for the additional existence of liquid water on the moon .
#Text=If water is confirmed this would be the first time liquid water is found outside of the Earth .
#Text=In other space news , NASA 's Phoenix Lander on Mars , which recently confirmed the presence of water ice on the planet , is analyzing a soil sample in its TEGA instrument today .
#Text=The results from the analysis are expected to establish whether the Martian soil contains perchlorates as earlier reports from the lander have indicated .
#Text=Andrea Thompson .
#Text=" Cassini Prepares for Monday Flyby of Saturn Moon " — SPACE.com , August 8 , 2008
